Job Requirements:
• At least 3 years of experience working with CNC Milling and Lathe machines;
• Graduated from a University or College with a related Metal Processing Technical major;
• Knowledge of CAD/ CAM/ CNC programming would be an advantage.
• Knowledge of AutoCAD and Inventor would also be an advantage.
• Experience with Fanuc/ KND system CNC controls;
• Able to communicate in the English language;
• Ability to work with engineering drawings, use gauges, pay attention to the manufacturing process, and apply analytical thinking;
• Good strength due to working with heavy product parts and heavy fixtures.
